source.name: 2010 Healthcare and Family Services Provider Data
source.description:
http://www2.illinois.gov/hfs/agency/Transparency/Pages/default.aspx

This data set provides information on the healthcare providers (including doctors, hospitals, and many others) who give healthcare services to the recipients of Medicaid and similar health benefit programs provided by the Illinois Department of Healthcare and Family Services. This data set is intended to be used along with the Healthcare and Family Services Provider ReadMe PDF available on data.illinois.gov.

For more information on this and other publicly available HFS data, please visit http://www2.illinois.gov/hfs/agency/Transparency/Pages/default.aspx
